snippet.title: C.H.A.I.N.G.E.D. - The world has ended -- time to make some choices!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://papercookies.itch.io/chainged?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt CHAINGED is a collaboration between devs from the HauntedPS1 community. Games were developed one after the other, with a choice at the end of each game leading to a game by another developer.

➡️ More from Adam Pype https://papercookies.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
➡️ More horror games https://itch.io/games/tag-horror?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt

#itchio #indiegames #horror

00:00 Intro 
01:59 Tape 1
10:23 Kyoto (Kyoto 1986)
17:28 Fight Antichrist (Showdown)
20:27 Confront Chronos (Loop Town)
27:12 Be Reborn (?)
48:36 Take Chronos' Power (The Unraveling)
54:16 Search for Lucy (Back Home)
57:15 Basement (Ouros)
59:08 Wyoming (What Lies in Wait)

1:11:32 Rescue Ezra (Executive Order)
1:23:41 Shoot (Deja Void)
1:28:22 Go Through Door (Transport Struggle)
